# Army builder
Army builder API is a *short texts saving* service similar to its physical paper presence on your table.

## Army Builder API Root [/]
Army builder API entry point.

This resource does not have any attributes. Instead it offers the initial API affordances in the form of the HTTP Link header and HAL links.
## Retrieve Entry Point [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/hal+json)
    + Headers
    
            Link: <https://api.shrikeh.net/>;rel="self"
            Last-Modified: Wed, 07 Apr 2014 23:31:27 GMT

    + Body

            {
                "_links": {
                    "self": {
                        "title": "Army builder index",
                        "href": "/"
                    },
                    "curies": [{
                        "name": "army-builder",
                        "href": "https://api.shrikeh.net/docs/{rel}",
                        "templated": true
                    }],
                    "army-builder:status": {
                        "title": "Status",
                        "href": "/status"
                    },
                    "army-builder:game-systems": {
                        "title": "Systems",
                        "href": "/game-systems"
                    },
                    "army-builder:game-system": {
                        "href": "/game-systems/{system}",
                        "templated": true
                    }
                    "army-builder:manufacturers": {
                        "title": "Manufacturers",
                        "href": "/manufacturers"
                    }
                }
            }

