## GameSystem [/game-systems/{game-system}]
A single System resource with all its details.
The System resource has the following attributes:

- name
- description
+ Parameters
    + game-system (required, game-system, `infinity`) ... String `game-system` of the GameSystem to query. Has example value.
    
+ Model (application/hal+json)
    HAL+JSON representation of GameSystem Resource. In addition to representing its state in the JSON form it offers affordances in the form of the HTTP Link header and HAL links.
    + Headers
    
            Link: <https://api.shrikeh.net/game-systems/infinity/>;rel="self"
            Last-Modified: Wed, 07 Jul 2010 23:31:27 GMT

    + Body
    
            { 
                "name": "Infinity",
                "description": "Infinity is a game with 28mm high metal miniatures that simulates combat and special operations in a science fiction environment with Manga aesthetics. Infinity miniatures are characterized by the high quality and detail of their modeling, the dynamism of their postures and their futuristic aesthetic.",
                "_links": {
                    "self": {
                        "title": "Infinity",
                        "href": "/game-systems/infinity"
                    },
                    "factions": {
                        "title": "Infinity: Factions"
                        "href": "/game-systems/infinity/factions"
                    }
                },
                "_embedded": {
                    "manufacturers": [{
                        "_links": {
                            "self": {
                                "title": "Corvus Belli",
                                "href": "/manufacturers/corvus-belli"
                            }
                        },
                        "name": "Corvus Belli",
                        "website": "http://www.corvusbelli.com",
                        "description": "Corvus Belli puts history and fantasy in your hands. Corvus Belli designs and manufacture s miniatures in white metal for collectors, painters, wargamers and role-playing games players. The miniatures are supplied without painting."
                    }]
